text: Erika Enzenhofer (born 2 September 1926) was an Austrian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1926 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Austrian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
